(we need to continue the ooc conversation. there's been a catastrophic loss of story continuity. the trio discussed future plans with holbrook and torres. they said they'd need a fourth member of their crew to be the brawn to their brains. holbrook recommended someone she knew who's heroic and morally-sound, matching the existing crew's style. dax requested torres do a full, deep background check to make sure she's not a double agent, then arrange for them to meet with the trio face-to-face to see if they'd be a good fit.
director also promised them a contract for them to run a research ship with full engineering, tech and medical suites to assist in retrieving archeological samples somewhere. i believe it was a 6 month period. but they'd have to resolve the current immediate threat from osprey first, and their other looming obligations around the post-incident investigations. but their larger fight with weyland will continue in the starts, for sure...
if any of this rings a bell, is still in memory, then keep the continuity. but can we make a little pocket of time where this discussion can happen again, so you log it in memory for real now? i fixed the backend so every message gets recorded)
